            "ORCID provides a persistent identifier - an ORCID iD - that distinguishes you from other researchers. Learn more at": "ORCID 提供持久標識符 - ORCID iD - 將您與其他開發人員區分，瞭解更多訊息請訪問",
            "Connect your ORCID iD": "關聯您的 ORCID iD",
