            "Disconnecting your ORCID iD may affect areas of your profile where your ORCID iD is displayed.": "解除關聯 ORCID iD 可能會影響您個人資料中顯示 ORCID iD 的區域。",
            "Disconnect your ORCID iD": "解除關聯您的 ORCID iD",
