                "When you're given access to": "當您獲得",
                "Dependabot alerts": "Dependabot 警報",
                "automatically receive notifications when a new vulnerability is found in one of your dependencies.": " 訪問權限時，當您的某個依賴項中發現新的漏洞時，就會自動收到通知。",

