                "Passwordless sign-in with passkeys": "使用通行金鑰進行無密碼登入",
                "Passkeys are webauthn credentials that validate your identity using touch, facial recognition, a device password, or a PIN. They can be used as a password replacement or as a 2FA method. Passkeys can be used for sign-in as a simple and secure alternative to your password and two-factor credentials.": "通行金鑰是一種 WebAuthn 憑證，可以使用觸摸、面部識別、設備密碼或 PIN 碼驗證您的身份。它們可以作為密碼替代品或作為雙因素身份驗證（2FA）方法使用。通行金鑰可以作為一種簡單且安全的替代方式用於登入，替代您的密碼和雙因素身份驗證憑證。",
                "This browser or device does not fully support passkeys - you may be able to use a passkey from another device.": "此瀏覽器或設備不完全支持通行金鑰 - 您可以嘗試使用來自其他設備的通行金鑰。",
