                "Review request": "審核請求",
                "Access public information (read-only)": "訪問公開訊息（只讀）",
                "Access user email addresses (read-only)": "訪問用戶電子電子郵件（只讀）",
                "Read all user profile data": "讀取所有用戶個人資料資料",
                "Create gists": "創建程式碼片段",
                "Full control of private repositories": "完全控制私有儲存庫",
                "Update github action workflows": "更新 GitHub Action 工作流",
                "Update all user data": "更新所有用戶資料",
