            "Want to build something that integrates with and extends GitHub?": "想要構建與 GitHub 集成和擴展的東西嗎？",
            "New GitHub App": "註冊新 GitHub 應用",
            "to get started developing on the GitHub API. You can also read more about building GitHub Apps in our": "，開始在 GitHub API 上進行開發。您還可以在我們的文件中閱讀更多關於構建 GitHub 應用的訊息",
            "developer documentation": "開發者文件",
