            "Identifying and authorizing users": "識別並授權用戶",
                "The full URL to redirect to after a user authorizes an installation.": "用戶授權安裝後重定向到的完整地址。",
                "Callback URL documentation": "回調地址文件",
                "Add Callback URL": "新增回調地址",

