            "Learn about pull requests": "瞭解合併請求",

            "Create pull request": "創建合併請求",

            "Compare and review just about anything": "比較和審查任何文件",
            "Branches, tags, commit ranges, and time ranges. In the same repository and across forks.": "分支，標籤，提交範圍和時間範圍。在同一儲存庫和復刻的儲存庫。",
            "Example comparisons": "比較例子",

            "Commit": "提交",
            "Commits": "提交",
