            "Actions repository access": "操作儲存庫訪問",
            "Pick the repositories that can access this package using GitHub Actions.": "選擇可以使用 GitHub Actions 訪問此軟件包的儲存庫。",
            "Permissions added for selected repositories.": "為選定的儲存庫新增了權限。",
            "Permissions updated for selected repositories.": "更新了選定儲存庫的權限。",
            "Can upload and download this package. Can read and write package metadata.": "可以上傳和下載此軟件包，並且可以讀取和寫入元資料。",
            "Can download this package and read package metadata.": "可以下載此軟件包並讀取元資料。",
            "Can upload, download, and manage this package. Can read and write package metadata. Can delete and restore packages.": "可以上傳、下載和管理此軟件包，可以讀取和寫入元資料，可以刪除和恢復此軟件包。",
            "Can upload, download, and manage this package. Can read and write package metadata. Can grant package permissions.": "可以上傳、下載和管理此軟件包，可以讀取和寫入元資料，可以授予軟件包權限。",
            "Manage Codespaces access": "程式碼空間訪問管理",
