                "Control how Dependabot opens pull requests, ignores false positives and snoozes alerts. Rules can be enforced at the organization level. Free for open source and available for private repos through": "控制 Dependabot 如何打開合併請求、忽略誤報和推遲警報。規則可以在組織層面強制執行。免費供開源專案使用，私有儲存庫需要通過",
                "GitHub Advanced Security.": "GitHub 高級安全性。",
                "Learn more about auto-triage": "瞭解更多關於自動分類的訊息",

