            "Sometimes conversations happen on old items that aren't yet closed. Here is a list of all the Issues and Pull Requests with unresolved conversations.": "有時對尚未關閉的舊專案會有新的討論。以下是所有有未解決討論的議題和合併請求列表。",
                "commented on": "評論於",
                "new comments": "新評論",

    },
    "regexp": [ // 正則翻譯
