            "Repository name": "儲存庫名稱",
            "Rename": "重命名",
                // [/is available./, "名稱可用。"],
                "The repository": "儲存庫",
                "already exists on this account.": "已經存在於此帳戶。",
                "Your new repository will be created as": "您的新儲存庫將被創建為",
                // 頂部提醒
                "Repository name was not changed": "儲存庫名稱未更改",

                "Renaming...": "重命名中…",

            "Template repository": "範本庫",
                "Template repositories let users generate new repositories with the same directory structure and files.": "範本儲存庫允許用戶生成具有相同目錄結構和文件的新儲存庫。",
                "A repository with LFS content cannot be used as a template.": "帶有 LFS 內容的儲存庫不能作為範本使用。",
                "Learn more about template repositories": "瞭解更多關於範本庫的訊息",

            "Commits": "提交",
                "Require contributors to sign off on web-based commits": "要求貢獻者在基於 Web 的提交上籤署",
                    "Enabling this setting will require contributors to sign off on commits made through GitHub’s web interface. Signing off is a way for contributors to affirm that their commit complies with the repository's terms, commonly the": "啟用此設置將要求貢獻者簽署通過 GitHub 的 Web 介面所做的提交。簽署是貢獻者確認他們的提交符合儲存庫條款的一種方式，通常是",
                    "Developer Certificate of Origin (DCO)": "開發者來源證書（DCO）",
                    "Learn more about signing off on commits": "瞭解更多關於簽署提交的訊息",
                "Allow comments on individual commits": "允許對單個提交發表評論",
                    "Enabling this setting will allow anyone who can view this repository to add": "啟用此設置後，任何能查看該儲存庫的人都可以新增",
                    "commit comments": "提交評論",
                    ". Existing commit comments are not affected by this setting and will remain viewable, editable, and deletable.": "。現有的提交評論不受此設置影響，依然可以查看、編輯和刪除",

            "This setting is enabled on the upstream repository. Disabling this setting may block commits from being merged upstream.": "此設置在上游儲存庫中啟用。禁用此設置可能會阻止提交向上遊合併。",

            "Default branch": "預設分支",
            "The default branch is considered the “base” branch in your repository, against which all pull requests and code commits are automatically made, unless you specify a different branch.": "預設分支被認為是儲存庫中的 “基礎” 分支，所有的合併請求和程式碼提交都是針對該分支進行的，除非您指定一個不同的分支。",
            "Rename branch": "重命名分支",
                // 重命名分支對話框
                "Rename this branch": "重命名分支",
                "Rename": "重命名",
                "to:": "為：",
                // [/is already the branch name./, "已經是分支的名稱了。"],
                // [/Your branch name will be/, "您的分支的名稱將重命名為"],
                "Most projects name the default branch": "大多數專案將預設分支名為",
                "Renaming this branch:": "重命名此分支：",
                    // 該分支存在來自其他分支的合併請求時
                        "Will update": "將更新",
                        "pull request targeting this branch.": "條針對該分支的合併請求。",
                        "pull requests targeting this branch.": "條針對該分支的合併請求。",
                        "branch protection rule that explicitly targets": "條分支保護規則明確針對",

                    // 該分支存在用於其他分支的合併請求時
                        "Will close": "將關閉",
                        "open pull request for this branch.": "個該分支的合併請求。",

                    // 重命名 GitHub Pages 所在分支
                        "Will unpublish current GitHub Pages site.": "將取消當前發布的 GitHub Pages 站點。",
                            "Your current GitHub Pages site will become unpublished. A new commit on the renamed branch will publish the GitHub Pages site again.": "您當前的 GitHub Pages 站點將被取消發布。重命名分支上的新提交將再次發布 GitHub Pages 站點。",

                    "Will not update your members' local environments.": "不會更新您成員的本地環境。",
                "Renaming this branch will not update your members' local environments.": "重命名此分支不會更新您成員的本地環境。",
                    "Your members will have to manually update their local environments. We'll let them know when they visit the repository, or you can share the following commands.": "您的成員將不得不手動更新他們的本地環境。我們會在他們訪問儲存庫時通知他們，或者您可以共享以下命令。",
                "Saving…": "保存中…",

            "Switch to another branch": "切換到另一分支",
                // 分支切換對話框
