                "are available.": "可用。",
            "Your Country/Region": "您的國家/地區",
                "Select Country/Region": "選擇國家/地區",
                "For compliance reasons, we're required to collect country information to send you occasional updates and announcements.": "根據合規要求，我們需要收集您所在的國家/地區訊息，以便向您發送最新的更新和公告。",

            "Email preferences": "電子郵件偏好設置",
                "Receive occasional product updates and announcements": "偶爾接收產品更新和公告",

            "Create account": "創建帳戶",
                "By creating an account, you agree to the": "創建帳戶即表示您同意",
                "Terms of Service": "服務條款",
                ". For more information about GitHub's privacy practices, see the": "。更多關於 GitHub 隱私條款的訊息，請參見",
