                "Building an application, service, or tool that integrates with GitHub?": "構建應用、服務或工具，集成到 GitHub 嗎？",
                "Join the GitHub Developer Program": "加入 GitHub 開發者計劃",
                ", or read more about it at our": "，或瞭解更多訊息在我們的",
