                "Check out the Developer site": "查看開發者站點，",
                "for guides, our API reference, and other resources for building applications that integrate with GitHub. Make sure your contact information is up-to-date below. Thanks for being a member!": "以獲取指南、我們的 API 參考和其他用於構建與 GitHub 集成的應用的資源。請確保您的聯繫訊息是最新的。感謝您成為我們的成員！",

