                    "Read the Standard Terms of Service": "閱讀 “標準服務條款”",
                "Corporate": "企業",
                    "Best for businesses that need to protect their intellectual property and secure visibility into their data.": "最適合需要保護知識產權並確保資料可見性的企業。",
