        "Codespace ownership": "程式碼空間所有權",
            "Control who owns codespaces created by your organization’s members on organization owned repositories. Codespace ownership dictates who is billed for usage, whose policies apply, and where audit logs are sent.": "控制誰擁有組織成員在組織擁有的儲存庫上創建的程式碼空間。程式碼空間所有權決定了由誰來支付使用費、適用誰的策略以及審計日誌發送到何處。",

