            // 頂部提醒
                "Failed to add secret. Secret names can only contain alphanumeric characters ([a-z], [A-Z], [0-9]) or underscores (_). Spaces are not allowed. Must start with a letter ([a-z], [A-Z]) or underscores (_).": "新增機密失敗。機密名稱只能包含字母數字字符（[a-z]、[A-Z]、[0-9]）或下劃線 (_)。不允許有空格。必須以字母 ([a-z], [A-Z]) 或下劃線 (_) 開頭。",
                "Secret added.": "機密已新增。",
