            "Template:": "範本：",
                "Templates": "範本",
                "None": "無",
                    "Start from scratch with a completely blank project board. You can add columns and configure automation settings yourself.": "從一個完全空白的專案面板開始。您可以自己新增欄目並配置自動化設置。",
