        // 高級篩選視窗
            "Advanced filters": "高級篩選",
                "Build complex filter queries": "建立複雜的篩選器查詢",
                "To start building your query add your first filter using the button below.": "要開始建立查詢，請使用下面的按鈕新增第一個篩選器。",

                "Qualifier": "限定",
