                        "Intro to GitHub": "GitHub 介紹",
                            "GitHub flow is a lightweight, branch-based workflow. In this Experience you'll learn the basics of the GitHub Flow including creating and making changes to branches within a repository, as well as creating and merging pull requests. The GitHub flow is useful for everyone, not just developers.": "GitHub 工作流是一種基於分支的輕量級工作流。在本體驗中，您將學習 GitHub 工作流的基礎知識，包括創建和修改版本庫中的分支，以及創建和合併合併請求。GitHub 工作流不僅對開發人員有用，對每個人都有用。",
